data.description: Are you looking for move in ready? This 1 year old home offers new construction feel with many upgrades. It is part of the Garden Cottages. A green space courtyard is shared by the owners and the association takes care of the lawn mowing and snow removal. From the inviting front porch you walk into the open concept living/dining/kitchen area. The kitchen has white cabinets with stainless steel appliances. You will also find a main floor bedroom and bath with shower and laundry area. Upstairs you will find two large bedrooms (15x14 and 12x23)with vaulted ceilings, walk in closets and a spacious bath. The walk in closets have custom organizers. Other upgrades/features of this home include: custom Levelor blinds throughout, luxury vinyl planking in living/dining/kitchen area, tile bathrooms, 3 panel interior doors, fully insulated garage and dimmer switches have been added to many lights. This property has a partial tax abatement for 5 years! Hurry to schedule your showing!
